  <brief_title>A Follow-up Study to Assess Resistance to ABT-072 in HCV-infected Subjects Administered ABT-072 in Prior ABT-072 Studies</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Follow-up Study to Assess the Evolution and Persistence of Resistance to ABT-072 After Discontinuation of ABT-072 Therapy in HCV Genotype-1 Infected Subjects Who Participated in Phase 1, 2, or 3 ABT-072 Clinical Studies</official_title>
  <sponsors>
