  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a follow-up study with no treatment and only samples being collected.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the development of specific viral mutations in
      response to treatment with ABT-072.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
